[1;33mUsage[m

  [1;32mwidgets inspect[m [31m[options][m [34m[<name>][m

    Without [34m<name>[m, lists every known widget.

    With [34m<name>[m, prints that widget's details. Pass [31m--verbose[m to
    include all fields, or use the [38;5;183mremove[m command to delete it.

[1;33mArguments[m

  [34m[<name>][m  Widget name to inspect

[1;33mOptions[m

  [31m-v[m, [31m--verbose[m  Show all fields

  [31m-h[m, [31m--help[m     Print help
